      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLYING SKIPPER (2) turned in a solid run last start over 400m at Warragul finishing 4th and beaten only 3 lengths (23.35). Has never been out of the money in three starts this course and distance. The form out of his last race has been franked. Has ability and looks hard to stop. RATTLE AND HUM (6) is a newcomer for the James Presutto kennel with no trial form to work with. Profiles well but prefer to see a move in betting. RIO DE JANEIRO (1) is on debut with a good inside draw a bonus. Bold showing expected here. SIGHT TO BEHOLD (7) makes debut for the David Jensen kennel. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Profiles nicely but market best guide to ability.",
